solution: ```class Solution {
    public List<List<Integer>> largeGroupPositions(String s) {
        List<List<Integer>> res = new ArrayList<>();
        int n = s.length();
        if (n < 3) return res;
        int start = 0;
        for (int i = 1; i <= n; i++) {
            if (i == n || s.charAt(i) != s.charAt(start)) {
                if (i - start >= 3) {
                    res.add(Arrays.asList(start, i - 1));
                }
                start = i;
            }
        }
        return res;
    }
}```
efficiency: HIGH
time complexity: O(n)
space complexity: O(1) excluding output
energy implications: LOW
explanation: Single linear scan tracking start of each group; when group ends, check length and record interval if ≥3. Minimal extra memory and CPU usage.

